sentences.sContent: And then, while the pretty brunette girl finished singing her verse, he buzzed me through like I was someone who mattered.
sentences.sContent_eng: And then, while the pretty brunette girl finished singing her verse, he buzzed me through like I was someone who mattered.
sentences.sCn: 那个黑发女孩唱完之后，他按了一下按钮就让我过去了，好像我是什么重要人物似的。
